{"tid":2461130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"BCI（更好的棉花組織）已經撤下針對新疆的公告","createTime":"2021-03-25T08:58:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T09:24:59.000Z","uid":391580,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"36dd9c763f9bb570c96bbe742f15b28e8664a644","tid":2461130,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T08:58:16.000Z","msg":"BCI去年10月發表的更新聲明指，由於中國新疆遭持續指控強迫勞動及侵犯人權，也由於強迫勞動會導致農場經營難以持續的風險不斷增加，BCI決定立即停止在新疆的所有農場活動，包括能力建設和數據監測及報告。<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">該聲明目前已從BCI網站撤下，暫不清楚具體撤下時間。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n原公告網址<br />\n<a href=\"https://bettercotton.org/bbc-news-report-on-xinjiang-bci-statement/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbettercotton.org%2Fbbc-news-report-on-xinjiang-bci-statement%2F&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2FnlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=e5e36055\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bettercotton.org/bbc-news-report-on-xinjiang-bci-statement/</a><br />\n<br />\n網絡backup版本<br />\n<a href=\"https://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache:trDlAZ9WInoJ:https://bettercotton.org/where-is-better-cotton-grown/china/announcement-bci-suspends-licensing-in-western-china/+&amp;cd=4&amp;hl=zh-CN&amp;ct=clnk&amp;gl=us\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebcache.googleusercontent.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dcache%3AtrDlAZ9WInoJ%3Ahttps%3A%2F%2Fbettercotton.org%2Fwhere-is-better-cotton-grown%2Fchina%2Fannouncement-bci-suspends-licensing-in-western-china%2F%2B%26cd%3D4%26hl%3Dzh-CN%26ct%3Dclnk%26gl%3Dus&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2FnlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=777868de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache:trDlAZ9WInoJ:https://bettercotton.org/where-is-better-cotton-grown/china/announcement-bci-suspends-licensing-in-western-china/+&amp;cd=4&amp;hl=zh-CN&amp;ct=clnk&amp;gl=us</a>"},{"pid":"8c2c6380e450a5930333294f82d004258190dc31","tid":2461130,"uid":362827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy